            <title>[WICKET-5999] AjaxFormValidatingBehavior not updates initially hidden feedback component</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5999</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve found that AjaxFormValidatingBehavior not updates any feedback component that was initially hidden (setOutputMarkupPlaceholderTag is set to true).&lt;/p&gt;

